net.proteusframework.ui.workspace

Class WorkspaceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.workspace.WorkspaceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Notifiable, Workspace

    @Configurable
public class WorkspaceImpl
extends Object
implements Workspace
    Default Workspace Implementation.
    To use, be sure to set:
    • A Notifiable such as MessageContainer.
    • A UITaskManager.
    • A task container. This is where the task UIs will be placed. The container must be initialized before using workspace.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
